&lt 5 ESC   &trans   &kp Z      &kp X     &kp C      &kp V     &trans  &kp B     &kp N            &kp M   &kp DELETE  &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL
&trans      &lt 5 A  &kp LSHFT  &kp LALT  &kp SPACE  &mo 1     &trans  &kp LEFT  &kp RIGHT_ARROW  &mo 2   &kp COMMA   &kp DOT
